Interface UserSupport

All Superinterfaces:
AccountEventsProvider
All Known Subinterfaces:

public interface UserSupport
extends AccountEventsProvider

This interface contains suporting methods, required by a user of the system.

listLastHistoryOrders2

Order2[] listLastHistoryOrders2(int accountId,
                                long fromIndex,
                                long tillIndex)
                                throws java.rmi.RemoteException
Returns historical list of the latest orders sent from the specified account, which are currently in a terminal state. Two indices (starting index and ending index) are specified to return a subset of the latest order list, which is useful for splitting a list in several pages.

tillIndex - ending index

listQuotesWithTicker

java.lang.Object[] listQuotesWithTicker(int accountId)
                                        throws java.rmi.RemoteException
This request is used to retrieve the latest available quotes for all subscribed instruments of the user, and a ticker value – the value of available equity (margin excess). It returns array of Quote structures with one entry per instrument, and a single number for ticker value. The ticker value is calculated for the account specified in request. Zero value is returned if zero or invalid account ID is specified in request.

Parameters:
accountId - account identifier
Returns:
array of two objects: Double and Quote[]
Throws:
java.rmi.RemoteException - in case of remote errors

getTicker

double getTicker(int accountId)
                 throws java.rmi.RemoteException
This request is used to retrieve the latest ticker value – available equity (margin excess) for the specified account. Zero value is returned if zero or invalid account number is specified.

Parameters:

available equity (margin excess)

Request to create a new alarm. AddAlarm request is used to add a new alarm for the user. Partially filled Alarm structure is passed as an argument with the following fields filled: Instrument ID Condition code Alarm price Notify via email flag Notify via SMS flag
